query:
SELECT
                    solutions.id,
                    solutions.code,
                    solutions.language,
                    challenges.judge,
                    solutions.time_out_count
                FROM solutions
                INNER JOIN challenges ON solutions.challenge = challenges.id
                WHERE ($1::text IS NULL OR solutions.language=$1::text) AND
                    ($2::integer IS NULL OR challenges.id=$2::integer) AND
                    solutions.valid
